\id JUD - Kaluli Bible
\h Yud
\toc1 Moęž‰foęž‰s We Yud E Saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰
\toc2 Yud
\toc3 Yud
\mt2 Moęž‰foęž‰s We
\mt1 Yud
\mt2 E Saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰
\imt1 Asulumaęž‰noęž‰ towoęž‰ we
\ip Moęž‰foęž‰s we Yud e saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, e Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ ao nowoęž‰ e. To eloęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s amiloęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ we, Bida eloęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s andeb saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰, heb 2 aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ to noloęž‰ imiloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.
\ip Yud eloęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s wenamiloęž‰ to alan sioęž‰woęž‰ we. Keliso kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ ini tilidabuwoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ domaęž‰ki sioęž‰. Kalu noloęž‰ mogagoęž‰woęž‰ dimidaki, Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ yoęž‰le dowaęž‰sen koęž‰loęž‰ iyoęž‰ saęž‰s usamioęž‰ oęž‰ma tindaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, madali towoęž‰ widaęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Keliso kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ ililoęž‰ man widab aęž‰noęž‰ kudu haęž‰nabenaęž‰ki, hagugu sioęž‰.
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1.1 \xt Madi 13.55\x*Ne Yud, Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ ene nanogdoęž‰ dian kaluwoęž‰ nowoęž‰ ne. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Yaęž‰maęž‰saęž‰ aowoęž‰ ne. Niyoęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s we Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ hoęž‰idaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰feyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale gimoęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰toęž‰l. Do Gode eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ mada alan asulaki, Yaęž‰su Keliso eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowaęž‰sen.
\v 2 Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ nofolaęž‰sen manoęž‰, haęž‰faęž‰nolo dowan manoęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰sen man aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ gi amioęž‰ ililitaęž‰gaęž‰ anamaęž‰ki, Godemoęž‰ dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l.
\s1 Gode eyoęž‰ madali toloęž‰ widaęž‰laboęž‰ falasilaęž‰maęž‰ib
\p 
\v 3 Ne milile, Gode eyoęž‰ nioęž‰ tambo aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ gasilimaęž‰kiloęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰soęž‰ tamina saęž‰saęž‰limaęž‰noęž‰ asuloęž‰. Koęž‰sega oęž‰goęž‰ niyoęž‰ to nowoęž‰ halale aęž‰saęž‰saęž‰limaęž‰noęž‰ asuloęž‰. To gililoęž‰ tilidabu aęž‰noęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰ dimi koęž‰loęž‰, to aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰liyoęž‰ moęž‰dowaki, koęž‰ngoęž‰ melaęž‰ib. Koęž‰sega kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ nodomaęž‰noęž‰ dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ gili asuloęž‰woęž‰ halale alitaki, to aęž‰noęž‰ dinafa boęž‰foęž‰meleaęž‰ki, to we aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰l.
\v 4 \x - \xo 1.4 \xt Gala 2.4, 2Bid 2.1\x*Moęž‰woęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ asulab aundoęž‰ moęž‰kudu haęž‰naęž‰sen kalu noloęž‰, gi oęž‰liaęž‰ gasamaęž‰niki woęž‰noęž‰le mioęž‰. Ili saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, â€śGode eyoęž‰ nioęž‰ alan asulakiyoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰sen koęž‰loęž‰, niliyoęž‰ uwoęž‰ dian man koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰li dimidaęž‰melaęž‰nikiâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰widoęž‰. Kalu i wemaęž‰yoęž‰ nili Alan Misaęž‰ kalu, Yaęž‰su Kelisowoęž‰ gola baęž‰daki, faęž‰s dimiaęž‰sen. Ililoęž‰ hala dimidaęž‰sen aęž‰noęž‰ falasilaęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰likiyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ bugoęž‰ amioęž‰ moęž‰lu saęž‰saęž‰li alifaęž‰.
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 1.5 \xt Kis 12.51, Nam 14.29-30\x*Kelegoęž‰ giloęž‰ tamin amiloęž‰ asululi aęž‰noęž‰ niyoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰asulumaęž‰ki saęž‰maęž‰nigoęž‰l. Alan eyoęž‰ Isolael kalukaęž‰isale enedoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ asuwaęž‰takiyoęž‰, Isib hen amiloęž‰ senoęž‰ tililiaęž‰gaęž‰, haęž‰laęž‰ya handalotaęž‰gaęž‰ ane. Koęž‰sega tif amioęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale e amiloęž‰ moęž‰tilidabu aęž‰noęž‰ yasalaęž‰.
\v 6 \x - \xo 1.6 \xt 2Bid 2.4\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ to we asuluma. Gode eyoęž‰ maęž‰mulaęž‰ kalu imoęž‰woęž‰ nanog inidoęž‰leyoęž‰ dimi koęž‰sega, noloęž‰ yoęž‰le dowaki, nanog imoęž‰loęž‰ dimi aęž‰noęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ane. Aęž‰laęž‰goęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ iyoęž‰ saęž‰niyaęž‰ melaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, sololi hen aęž‰na melaęž‰noęž‰ meleaęž‰ki disaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, iyoęž‰ hoęž‰len alan Godeyaęž‰ enedoęž‰ moęž‰walilimaęž‰nigab aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ yasilaęž‰lab.
\v 7 \x - \xo 1.7 \xt Moęž‰moęž‰ 19.1-25, 2Bid 2.6,10\x*Aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ goęž‰ oęž‰leaumboęž‰, Sodom, Gomola amisaęž‰n oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ amisaęž‰n nol anib amiloęž‰ kandayoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ asuluma. Kalukaęž‰isale i aęž‰noęž‰ uwoęž‰ diaki, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ uwoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰dimidan aumboęž‰loęž‰ dimidaęž‰len. Kalukaęž‰isale noloęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ falasilaęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ asulufoęž‰meleaęž‰kiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ amisaęž‰n kalukaęž‰isale i aęž‰noęž‰ falasilaki, de hen melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab aęž‰na taęž‰foęž‰.
\p 
\v 8 Aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ goęž‰ oęž‰leaumboęž‰, kalu giloęž‰ sab usamiloęž‰ woęž‰noęž‰ledoęž‰ mioęž‰ i aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, inidoęž‰ ofolab aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰, ini doęž‰moęž‰waęž‰yoęž‰ man mogagoęž‰le dimidaęž‰sen. Iyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰iyaki, yoęž‰le dowaęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ iliyoęž‰ maęž‰mulaęž‰ kalu halaidoęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ dioęž‰ge saęž‰laęž‰sen.
\v 9 \x - \xo 1.9 \xt Dan 10.13,21, 12.1, Sek 3.2, 2Bid 2.11, Kala 12.7\x*Koęž‰sega tamin amioęž‰ maęž‰mulaęž‰ kaluwaęž‰ misaęž‰ Maikoęž‰l eyoęž‰ Moęž‰saęž‰saęž‰ doęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ tadowoęž‰laki, Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ towaęž‰yoęž‰ kegab amioęž‰, Maikoęž‰l eyoęž‰ Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰ emoęž‰woęž‰, â€śGe mogagoęž‰ dimidabâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ moęž‰gadi sioęž‰. Koęž‰sega Maikoęž‰l eyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰, â€śAlan, eyoęž‰ gemoęž‰woęž‰ towoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ saęž‰maęž‰ibâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰ka sioęž‰.
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 1.10 \xt 2Bid 2.12\x*Koęž‰sega kalu i wemaęž‰yoęž‰ kelegoęž‰ iloęž‰ moęž‰fanda asululiab aęž‰noęž‰ dioęž‰ge saęž‰laęž‰sen. Kalu i wemaęž‰yoęž‰ asuloęž‰woęž‰ noęž‰ henaęž‰ usamiloęž‰ sab oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰ dowaki, inin doęž‰moęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰noęž‰koęž‰ fanda asulab. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ man aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ ininoęž‰ mada hendele mogagilaęž‰.
\v 11 \x - \xo 1.11 \xt Moęž‰moęž‰ 4.7-8, Nam 16.1-35, 2Bid 2.15, 1Yoęž‰n 3.12\x*Wai! Kalu i wenamioęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰woęž‰ alan faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ib. Moęž‰woęž‰ iyoęž‰ Kaęž‰inaęž‰ manoęž‰ kudu haęž‰naboęž‰loęž‰kaęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Balam eloęž‰ hala dimidoęž‰ oęž‰leaumboęž‰, iliyoęž‰loęž‰ moleyoęž‰ alan diaęž‰noęž‰ meselaęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Kola eyoęž‰ Moęž‰saęž‰s oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰iyaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, e aęž‰na sowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, kalu i wemaęž‰yoęž‰loęž‰ Gode oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰iyab koęž‰loęž‰ iyoęž‰ somaęž‰ib.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 1.12 \xt 2Bid 2.13,17\x*Gioęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰sen man aęž‰noęž‰ asulaki, maęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ maęž‰ni kegeaęž‰likiyoęž‰, kalu i we naęž‰bo amiloęž‰ doęž‰mo oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowaki, iliyoęž‰ man gililoęž‰ dimidab aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰molo asulaki, gioęž‰ oęž‰li mogagilaęž‰maęž‰ib. Iliyoęž‰ ini koęž‰ asulaęž‰sen. Kol koęž‰loęž‰ hoęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰tindakiloęž‰ fufayaęž‰loęž‰ tabeliaęž‰gane oęž‰leaumboęž‰, iyoęž‰loęž‰ inin nanog hendeleyoęž‰ moęž‰dimidoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, oęž‰ngoęž‰maloęž‰ngoęž‰ dowab. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ iyoęž‰ i koęž‰loęž‰ foloęž‰ helemaęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰len amiloęž‰ moęž‰hedan oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowoęž‰. Iyoęž‰ mada sowoęž‰le koęž‰loęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, i aęž‰noęž‰ bisoęž‰waęž‰yoęž‰ dudaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ sandifoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, mada olaliaki, sowoęž‰le koęž‰loęž‰lab.
\v 13 Kalu iyoęž‰ soęž‰lu hoęž‰n koęž‰loęž‰ ene asuloęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰yakiloęž‰ gululiaęž‰yab oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowaki, sendelomaęž‰noęž‰ man ililoęž‰woęž‰ hoęž‰n tubaęž‰s koęž‰loęž‰ dibidaęž‰sen oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowoęž‰. Iyoęž‰ akin amiloęž‰ tamin moęž‰gelakiloęž‰ babale siaęž‰sen oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowoęž‰. Gode eyoęž‰ hen sololi nowoęž‰ iyoęž‰ aęž‰na melaęž‰noęž‰ meleaęž‰ki dimidaefaęž‰.
\p 
\v 14-15 \x - \xo 1.14-15 \xt Moęž‰moęž‰ 5.18,21-24\x*Inog eyoęž‰ kalu i we koęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, tamina dinali sioęž‰. Inog e, Adamaęž‰ e soęž‰loęž‰wa aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ ageloęž‰woęž‰ domoęž‰ e koęž‰loęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰. Inog eyoęž‰ dinali saęž‰lakiyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰, â€śBoęž‰ba! Alan e ene maęž‰mulaęž‰ kalu modoęž‰ daosen aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ yakiyoęž‰, kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ tambo moęž‰walilimaęž‰ni yab. Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ asulab aundoęž‰ moęž‰kudu haęž‰naęž‰sen kalukaęž‰isale ililoęž‰ mogagoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ dimidaęž‰len aęž‰noęž‰ tambo alobaęž‰daki falasilaęž‰maęž‰ib. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ to mogagoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ ililoęž‰ emoęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰len aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ tambo Alan eyoęž‰ alobaęž‰daki, waęž‰demaęž‰ni yabâ€ť Inog eyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dinali sioęž‰.
\v 16 Kalu i wemaęž‰yoęž‰ nolboęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰beaki, digaęž‰lilaęž‰sen. Inin doęž‰moęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ sagalemaęž‰noęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰sen. Iyoęž‰ kailaki, inin wiyoęž‰ duludaęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ iyoęž‰ enedoęž‰ asulab aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ diaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰lakiyoęž‰, kalu nolboęž‰woęž‰ safaęž‰ to saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, haęž‰nolo saęž‰laęž‰sen. \fig Kalukaęž‰isale moęž‰walilimaęž‰nikiyoęž‰, Yaęž‰su e ene maęž‰mulaęž‰ kalu oęž‰liaęž‰ miaęž‰ib.|alt="Jesus in cloud" src="41_Mk_16_09_RG_gr.tif" size="col" copy="Â© Sweet Publishing http://sweetpublishing.com, licensed under a CC: BY-SA 3.0 Unported licence." ref="1.14"\fig*
\s1 Ginin tilidabuwoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ dowaęž‰bi
\p 
\v 17 Tamin amioęž‰ nili Alan Yaęž‰su Keliso eloęž‰ iligaęž‰feloęž‰ kalu iliyoęž‰, kelegoęž‰ tif amiloęž‰ oęž‰faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ towoęž‰ dinali saefaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, ni milile gioęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ waęž‰ka asulaęž‰bi.
\v 18 \x - \xo 1.18 \xt 2Bid 3.3\x*Iliyoęž‰ gimoęž‰ saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, â€śElemaęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowalikiyoęž‰, dioęž‰ge saęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ kaluwoęž‰ aęž‰na faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ib koęž‰loęž‰, iliyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ asulab aundoęž‰ moęž‰kudu haęž‰naki, asuloęž‰ mogagoęž‰ inidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰ib.â€ť Iligaęž‰feloęž‰ kalu iliyoęž‰ towoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰saefaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ giliyoęž‰ asulaęž‰bi.
\v 19 Gioęž‰ gegeleboęž‰ moęž‰ege domaęž‰kiyoęž‰, kalu i wemaęž‰yoęž‰ gioęž‰ digene meab amioęž‰ alobaęž‰daęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ iyoęž‰ henfeloęž‰ mande aęž‰noęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰sen koęž‰loęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ Mama Maliloęž‰woęž‰ i oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰dowaęž‰sen.
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 1.20 \xt Kolo 2.7\x*Koęž‰sega ni milile, a halaidoęž‰ dian oęž‰leaumboęž‰, tilidabu maliloęž‰ gililoęž‰woęž‰ halaidoęž‰ domaęž‰ki, diaęž‰li haęž‰naęž‰lubi. Giliyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ Mamayaęž‰loęž‰ asulab au kudu haęž‰naki dulugu saęž‰laęž‰lubi.
\v 21 Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man us aęž‰na dowaęž‰bi. Alan Yaęž‰su Keliso eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ nofolaki, melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ dimiaęž‰ib koęž‰loęž‰, aęž‰noęž‰ asulakiyoęž‰ yasilaęž‰lubi.
\v 22 Giliyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale tilidabuwoęž‰ halaidoęž‰loęž‰ma dowab aęž‰noęž‰ nofolaki, haęž‰sa tililiaęž‰bi.
\v 23 \x - \xo 1.23 \xt Sek 3.2, Kala 3.4\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale noloęž‰ oęž‰ma de hena ane oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowab koęž‰loęž‰, giliyoęž‰ i aęž‰noęž‰ boęž‰boęž‰ge aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ gasilima. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ helebesoęž‰g heyab amiloęž‰ kaluwaęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰beab oęž‰leaumboęž‰, giliyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale noloęž‰ tagilaki, man mogagoęž‰ ilidoęž‰ dimidaęž‰sen aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰beakiyoęž‰ koęž‰naęž‰ dowaęž‰bi. Koęž‰sega giliyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale i koęž‰ nofolaki asuwaęž‰taęž‰lubi.
\s1 Godeyaęž‰ wiyoęž‰ dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l
\m 
\v 24 Gioęž‰ sulufoęž‰ ti haęž‰nabenaęž‰kiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ oęž‰li boęž‰foęž‰lowaęž‰sen. Eyoęž‰ gililoęž‰ hala dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ halaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, gioęž‰ digaloęž‰ kalu dowabiki, ene hoęž‰len alan maliloęž‰ us aęž‰na tililiaęž‰ yab amioęž‰, gioęž‰ sagalaęž‰liki kagamaęž‰ib koęž‰loęž‰, ene wiyoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰maęž‰niki.
